title: 6-7am- Scary Deep Fakes & the Turkey Shortage

description: Salman Rushdie is still recovering from being stabbed, there is a scary deep fake of Tom Cruise, Black Adam opened with 67 million dollars, Ticket to Paradise movie opened with 16 million, It’s cooling down and we might get rain, the World Series is set, a guy left voicemails for a hitman but dialed the wrong number, a startup in Russia is offering to bury people alive and dig them back up to see what it’s like, there is a big turkey shortage right now, and Vinnie reads your texts!
